WEBVTT

00:43.052 --> 00:44.803
I'm a dangerous man.

00:46.763 --> 00:48.471
When I get hell-bent
on something,

00:48.473 --> 00:49.473
I can be,

00:50.391 --> 00:51.392
downright mean.

00:55.022 --> 00:56.564
I get over zealous and,

00:58.359 --> 01:00.524
I can be forgetful of others,

01:00.526 --> 01:02.737
insensitive to their pain.

01:04.447 --> 01:07.115
It's my experience that,

01:07.117 --> 01:09.826
zeal is,

01:09.828 --> 01:15.498
the most dangerous characteristic
a man can possess.

01:15.500 --> 01:16.584
There's no talking to zeal.

01:18.753 --> 01:21.922
Now, all I need to
do is get a name.

01:21.924 --> 01:24.257
All you need to
do is give me one.

01:24.259 --> 01:26.968
I have a way of doing things.

01:26.970 --> 01:28.719
There's an order to it.

01:28.721 --> 01:30.721
I used to ask questions first.

01:30.723 --> 01:32.933
Before the nails, I mean.

01:32.935 --> 01:35.684
I would ask, and they would lie,

01:35.686 --> 01:37.854
then I'd have to nail
them to the table,

01:37.856 --> 01:41.900
and start all over again
asking my questions.

01:41.902 --> 01:43.527
I'm a busy man,

01:43.529 --> 01:44.527
time is gold,

01:44.529 --> 01:46.822
you understand.

01:46.824 --> 01:49.576
So now, I always
start with the nails.

02:12.057 --> 02:13.142
Pardon my grin.

02:44.797 --> 02:46.214
Clarence.

02:46.216 --> 02:48.216
Thanks for coming
to the house, bro.

02:48.218 --> 02:49.551
Sit down.

02:49.553 --> 02:50.844
And these
children are beautiful.

02:50.846 --> 02:52.387
I can't believe Mina.

02:52.389 --> 02:53.972
She's turning sixteen.

02:53.974 --> 02:55.849
We're gonna have a big party.

02:55.851 --> 02:57.058
Cigar?

02:57.060 --> 02:58.145
No, no thanks.

03:03.484 --> 03:04.484
So?

03:06.611 --> 03:08.197
You're not gonna like this.

03:17.706 --> 03:19.580
You want me to take care of it?

03:19.582 --> 03:21.084
No, you've done your part.

03:24.713 --> 03:26.048
Let's get you paid my bro.

03:33.180 --> 03:34.513
How much
money are you keeping,

03:34.515 --> 03:35.639
