03:37.226 --> 03:38.600
It's just not safe.

03:38.602 --> 03:39.935
I've told you that before.

03:39.937 --> 03:41.811
Mother hen, always watchful.

03:41.813 --> 03:43.646
Relax, this is collection night.

03:43.648 --> 03:45.899
This all going back
to Norik's house.

03:45.901 --> 03:47.859
So he
sends his own people?

03:47.861 --> 03:49.069
At the end of every week.

03:49.071 --> 03:50.403
On a motorcycle, no less.

03:50.405 --> 03:51.321
My nephew.

03:53.909 --> 03:55.577
Very fast, very efficient.

03:57.246 --> 03:58.956
Thank you for
everything, my friend.

04:00.332 --> 04:01.539
Enough business,

04:01.541 --> 04:03.750
