something very beautiful.

04:07.588 --> 04:10.048
I have had this made,

04:10.050 --> 04:12.177
for Mina for her
sixteenth birthday.

04:13.636 --> 04:15.345
She's a very special girl.

04:15.347 --> 04:17.555
I spared no expense.

04:17.557 --> 04:20.433
Norik knows this
diamond guy in Burbank.

04:20.435 --> 04:22.727
He's going to put
the center stone.

04:22.729 --> 04:24.187
It's going back to
him for finishing.

04:29.194 --> 04:29.985
How lovely.

04:39.955 --> 04:42.291
Alright, home sweet home.

04:44.585 --> 04:47.377
Wow, this is a nice place.

04:47.379 --> 04:49.045
