07:04.765 --> 07:07.934
So, when you say you
wanna do one of them,

07:07.936 --> 07:09.853
I think it's pretty
goddamn righteous.

07:15.318 --> 07:17.776
Well let's do it then.

07:17.778 --> 07:21.364
You know, ripping off
hipsters and frats boys is,

07:21.366 --> 07:23.575
