for this rinky dink shit.

07:29.207 --> 07:30.290
Bonnie?

07:30.292 --> 07:32.584
Parker.

07:32.586 --> 07:34.461
And that's just how
you'll end up, too sweety.

07:34.463 --> 07:35.712
Life's not a movie.

07:35.714 --> 07:36.754
You sure?

07:36.756 --> 07:38.089
It's got tragedy
written all over it.

07:38.091 --> 07:39.924
It's a bank, it's
not a scared kid.

07:39.926 --> 07:42.928
With a bank, you
don't plan it right,

07:42.930 --> 07:44.471
if you're unlucky,

07:44.473 --> 07:46.681
you can loose everything.

07:46.683 --> 07:49.058
My father was killed in a bank
robbery, you know that right.

07:49.060 --> 07:50.645
Okay forget banks, then.

07:51.688 --> 07:52.688
How about a,

07:54.733 --> 07:55.776
