13:02.958 --> 13:03.958
Yeah.

13:05.044 --> 13:06.044
By the way,

13:08.213 --> 13:09.965
sorry about Ann.

13:11.216 --> 13:14.843
Oh yeah well.

13:14.845 --> 13:16.179
Everybody's gotta die right.

13:17.555 --> 13:19.305
