die, we gotta die.

13:19.307 --> 13:22.141
You feel sad about that you
gotta be sad about everything,

13:22.143 --> 13:23.811
you know what I mean?

13:23.813 --> 13:25.103
Yeah.

13:26.397 --> 13:28.190
Look at the talk
I'm giving you.

