Hey Boe, you want a beer?

14:17.116 --> 14:18.406
A beer?

14:18.408 --> 14:19.908
Yeah.

14:19.910 --> 14:20.995
You got it.

15:13.130 --> 15:15.172
Oh I see you found the olives.

15:15.174 --> 15:16.339
