15:21.262 --> 15:23.347
You'll get your bearings.

15:23.349 --> 15:25.598
You get on a
schedule, a routine.

15:25.600 --> 15:26.557
Get a hobby.

15:26.559 --> 15:28.684
Millions of channels on the TV.

15:28.686 --> 15:31.230
Did you get TV in the
can at the end there?

15:31.232 --> 15:33.314
Yeah some.

15:33.316 --> 15:36.193
Well I'm gonna turn you
on to a lot of new programs.

15:36.195 --> 15:37.693
You ever hear of Net flick?

15:37.695 --> 15:38.695
No.

15:39.823 --> 15:41.658
Movies in the mail.

15:44.411 --> 15:45.660
Oh, by the way,

15:45.662 --> 15:48.080
you gotta see your
parole officer this week?

15:48.082 --> 15:49.372
Yeah Monday.

15:49.374 --> 15:51.041
What does he
expect you to do till then?

15:51.043 --> 15:53.835
Well they gave me gate money,

15:53.837 --> 15:56.338
