16:08.143 --> 16:09.392
Oh yeah.

16:09.394 --> 16:11.812
Lots of swell advice.

16:11.814 --> 16:13.480
Dirt bags.

16:13.482 --> 16:15.481
Don't worry, pal. I'm
gonna take care of you,

16:15.483 --> 16:17.903
