going for 500 dollars.

17:37.316 --> 17:39.816
I'll never forget you for that.

17:39.818 --> 17:41.860
You're welcome Artie.

17:55.834 --> 17:58.001
What does it say?

17:58.003 --> 17:59.004
Go to bed.

18:02.799 --> 18:04.009
Here we are.

18:09.555 --> 18:13.433
